text: Milbertshofen-Am Hart (Central Bavarian: Muibatshofa-Am Hoart) is a borough in the north of Munich in Germany. The three boroughs Milbertshofen, Am Riesenfeld and Am-Hart formed to create Milbertshofen-Am Hart. As of January 2020 it had a population of 76,670. == References == Category:Boroughs of Munich
